dataLineage.statement:
2015: Initial neighborhood boundaries delineated by public consensus per Bostonography crowdsourcing project
http://bostonography.com/2012/crowdsourced-neighborhood-boundaries-part-one-consensus
2016: Crowdsourced boundaries adjusted by the City of Somerville Planning Division to conform in part to Census block boundaries and public transportation infrastructure
2017: GIS dataset formalized and attributed by the City of Somerville GIS Coordinator
